{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Clamb is a punishing VR climbing game inspired by the game '<i>Getting Over It</i>'. You climb a surreal mountain with nothing but a hammer. The hammer follows the movement of your controllers. Hit, push and drag your hammer past obstacles to get over them. It will be difficult at first, but practice makes perfect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Climb a surreal mountain that reaches into the stratosphere.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> No checkpoints will save you from falling.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Your skills will be tested, your limits broken.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Tunnelling available to alleviate motion sickness. (Vignette)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Option to swap hands on the hammer.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> There is a reward for those who reach the top.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>I know it's quite a clamber up those rocks, but once you get to the top, the view is worth it.</i> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709120/extras/GIF_Climb.gif?t=1735579292\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>It's not the mountain we conquer, but ourselves.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Experiencing Issues?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For the best experience, ensure your VR runtime is set to default settings and properly configured. Most issues, such as physics problems or tracking errors, are caused by external software or misconfigurations. This is a common challenge with PCVR games, as the open nature of the platform can sometimes lead to conflicts. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Need help?</strong> Check the pinned troubleshooting guides in the Steam forums for quick fixes and setup instructions.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/